Hello, thank you for calling Harmony Music School. My name is Joseph Gonzales. How can I assist you today?

Hi, my name is Catherine Price. I'm calling about returning some sheet music I bought recently.

I'm sorry to hear that you're considering a return, Catherine. Could you let me know the reason for the return?

Sure, I just feel a bit overwhelmed with the music pieces and I think I might need to start with something simpler.

I understand. We certainly want you to feel comfortable with your music learning journey. Could I have the order number for the purchase, please?

Of course, it's one two three four five.

Thank you. I'll just need to confirm your email address associated with the order to process this return.

It's catherine.price@email.com.

Perfect, I have everything I need. I will process this return for you right away, Catherine. Is there anything else I can help with?

No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Joseph.

You're very welcome, Catherine. Thank you for contacting Harmony Music School. We hope to see you again soon. Have a great day!
